Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MC大奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  提案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的学园祭演唱会要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会要？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.90,0:00:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠MC活跃气氛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该靠演奏来活跃气氛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏自然也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但根据我在暗中进行的问卷调查中显示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家最希望在轻音部看到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑话！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都给谁做的问卷调查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让最搞笑的部员来担当MC吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始进行第一回MC大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？ 从我开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:01:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎大家…来到放学后茶会的…演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写成演唱会  其实读作平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边都很热闹…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷场了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NETA还不太行啊

